 |archivedate=2015-11-23 
}}</ref>词汇关联除了侦查影响词以外，还附于词汇一个和某项情绪的“关联”值。<ref name ="Stevenson">{{cite journal
 | first1 = Ryan
 | last1 = Stevenson
 | first2 = Joseph
 | last2 = Mikels
 | first3 = Thomas
 | last3 = James
 | title = Characterization of the Affective Norms for English Words by Discrete Emotional Categories
 | year = 2007
 | journal = Behavior Research Methods
 | volume = 39
